title: Kuinemangale
text: Kuinemangale is a <a href="Village%20development%20committee%20%28Nepal%29">village development committee</a> in <a href="Myagdi%20District">Myagdi District</a> in the <a href="Dhaulagiri%20Zone">Dhaulagiri Zone</a> of western-central <a href="Nepal">Nepal</a>. At the time of the <a href="1991%20Nepal%20census">1991 Nepal census</a> it had a population of 1650 people living in 290 individual households.
